Class EV3Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • ev3dev.sensors.EV3Key

  • public class EV3Key
extends java.lang.Object
    Provide a simple implementation to detect if any button is pressed. Note: It is necessary to review in next iteration how to manage better the buttons.
